        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8629",
        "content": "\"Oh, the fairy tale!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8629_261140_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8629/261140/8629_261140_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8629",
        "content": "\"When I left my dead mother's side I was in such a state of mind that I passed with scarcely so much as a glance the room where my new found father sat sleeping.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8629_261140_000015_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8629/261140/8629_261140_000015_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8629",
        "content": "But I did not turn away.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8629_261140_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8629/261140/8629_261140_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8629",
        "content": "This feeling was shared by others, and a reaction set in in Frederick's favour, which even affected the officials who were conducting the inquiry.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8629_261140_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8629/261140/8629_261140_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8629",
        "content": "Of the questions and answers which now passed between him and the various members of the jury I need give no account.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8629_261140_000019_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8629/261140/8629_261140_000019_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8629",
        "content": "For, however other people might feel, she did not for a moment believe his story.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8629_261140_000019_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8629/261140/8629_261140_000019_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8629",
        "content": "She had not a pure enough heart to do so.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8629_261140_000019_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8629/261140/8629_261140_000019_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8629",
        "content": "To her all self sacrifice was an anomaly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8629_261140_000019_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8629/261140/8629_261140_000019_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8629",
        "content": "No woman of the mental or physical strength of Agatha Webb would plant a dagger in her own breast just to prevent another person from committing a crime, were he lover, husband, or son.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8629_261140_000019_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8629/261140/8629_261140_000019_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8629",
        "content": "Yet how thrilling it had been to hear him plead his cause so well!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8629_261140_000019_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8629/261140/8629_261140_000019_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8629",
        "content": "It was almost worth the loss of her revenge to meet his look of hate, and dream of the possibility of turning it later into the old look of love.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
